    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A New Dream</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ruya: Ascension is a meditative puzzle game and sequel to the original award-winning game.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Caught in a time loop, Ruya visits different universes freeing lost souls by giving parts of herself away in order to attempt to unlock her past memories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ruya: Ascension presents a brand-new adventure set in a surreal plane of existence, featuring numerous new puzzles that build upon the experience of the original hit game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230930/extras/828585f35b798658b5f93ed713acf272.avif?t=1745243832\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230930/extras_big/828585f35b798658b5f93ed713acf272.avif?t=1745243832 width=800 height=57 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 handmade puzzles to make you ponder.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brand new puzzle pieces expanding on the original game. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 chapters to visit each with their own unique setting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An undo feature to help resolve past mistakes and work through solutions.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An illustrated narrative that unfolds as you progress. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enrico Ercole is back! With his original music, mix of live instruments and handcrafted audio.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230930/extras/828585f35b798658b5f93ed713acf272.avif?t=1745243832\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230930/extras_big/828585f35b798658b5f93ed713acf272.avif?t=1745243832 width=800 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230930/extras/c3af72a151f79b64590ed6f2c99ee86c.poster.avif?t=1745243832\" width=620 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230930/extras/c3af72a151f79b64590ed6f2c99ee86c.webm?t=1745243832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230930/extras/c3af72a151f79b64590ed6f2c99ee86c.mp4?t=1745243832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230930/extras/d909f0ca98c9c65687e7bc985a623f61.poster.avif?t=1745243832\" width=618 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230930/extras/d909f0ca98c9c65687e7bc985a623f61.webm?t=1745243832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230930/extras/d909f0ca98c9c65687e7bc985a623f61.mp4?t=1745243832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230930/extras/668b8dfefe85a18ab98e9193731ede07.poster.avif?t=1745243832\" width=620 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230930/extras/668b8dfefe85a18ab98e9193731ede07.webm?t=1745243832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230930/extras/668b8dfefe85a18ab98e91